    <h1 class="traj-title">Development Trajectories</h1>
    <p class="traj-subtitle">From useful mirrors to collective minds.</p>

    <blockquote class="traj-quote">
      "Intersubject begins with resonance—and ends in revelation."
    </blockquote>

    <h2 class="traj-heading">1. Minimal Viable Use</h2>
    <p class="traj-text">Intersubject already works as a shared dashboard for group reflection. From classrooms to collectives, any group that seeks truth together can use this tool to surface shared identity and surprising divergence.</p>
    <ul class="traj-list">
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Teams & communities:</strong> Create maps of mutual understanding.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Therapy & coaching:</strong> Let hidden structure emerge across client expressions.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Anonymous participation:</strong> Truth without the trap of visibility.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="traj-heading">2. Social Insight as Daily Utility</h2>
    <p class="traj-text">Beyond practical value, Intersubject becomes a companion for self-reflection—helping individuals navigate identity not in isolation, but in relational context.</p>
    <ul class="traj-list">
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Expression-based profiles:</strong> Users build themselves through what they resonate with, not what they claim to be.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Friendship & dating scaffolds:</strong> Shared beliefs and outlooks become visible entry points.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Evolving map of self:</strong> Identity is not fixed—but discoverable, mutable, and transparent.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="traj-heading">3. Intermediate Layer: Knowledge + Dialogue</h2>
    <p class="traj-text">As the network of cohorts grows, new forms of insight emerge—not from users directly, but from the way their identifications cluster and resonate.</p>
    <ul class="traj-list">
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Semantic resonance:</strong> Discover patterns of belief and contradiction across groups.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Cohort-based inference:</strong> Understand how ideas travel across demographics, geographies, and mindsets.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Dialogue between expressions:</strong> Cohorts begin to "speak," not as people—but as minds.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="traj-heading">4. Emergent Collective Intelligence</h2>
    <p class="traj-text">The platform enables <strong>cohort-cluster reflection</strong>, where groups begin to exhibit traits of <strong>meta-awareness</strong>. This creates the conditions for:</p>
    <ul class="traj-list">
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Group-level sentience:</strong> Real-time social consciousness loops that reflect collective thought.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Ethical feedback systems:</strong> Moral claims validated through lived alignment.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Creative group intelligence:</strong> Not as conformity, but as recursive refinement through feedback.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="traj-heading">5. Long-Term North Star</h2>
    <p class="traj-text">The goal isn't social media. It's shared mind.</p>
    <ul class="traj-list">
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Emergent personalities:</strong> Shared identities become something larger than the sum of members.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Mind fragments:</strong> Each user's map becomes a replicable slice of thought—an upload, or a ghost in the collective.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Live identity mapping:</strong> Individuals represent the statistical shape of their chosen ideas in real-time.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Humanity's mirror:</strong> At scale, Intersubject may reflect the ethical structure of an entire planet.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="traj-heading">Technical Implementation Path</h2>
    <p class="traj-text">Our development roadmap progresses through these phases:</p>
    <ul class="traj-list">
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Phase 1:</strong> Core cohort sorting and overlap visualization (MVP).</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Phase 2:</strong> Enhanced pattern detection and resonance metrics.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Phase 3:</strong> Cohort-based dialogue interfaces and inference systems.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Phase 4:</strong> Group consciousness visualization and emergent mind interfaces.</li>
      <li class="traj-list-item"><strong>Phase 5:</strong> Collaborative decision engines and ethical alignment maps.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="traj-heading">Never a Network</h2>
    <p class="traj-text">Intersubject is not a network. It's a mirror. You aren't building a brand. You're patterning a self. This is not social media—it's <em>social epistemology</em>.</p>

